title: Lovely 1 Bedroom Apartment… Waiting for You to Make it Home
posting_body: ['Mallard Ridge features: Community room, 24-hour fitness center, 2 pools, pet friendly, walk-in closets, central air, in unit washer and dryers and a patio or balcony!', 'These bright and spacious 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom floor plans – 960 square feet – are available for September and October!', 'Mallard Ridge is in a fantastic location with access to the best of what Maple Grove has to offer; shopping, lakes, trails, community center, library, entertainment, and more!', 'Located just off of Weaver Lake & Elm Creek, you have easy access to Hwy 94; just minutes from downtown Minneapolis.', 'Today, our best price on these one bedroom apartment is $1,695 when you sign an 18 month lease.', 'Water, trash, garage, and storage included!', 'Pricing, lease terms and availability are determined by requested move-in date and are subject to change at any time.', 'Please note that as our apartment homes tend to lease quickly...Schedule your appointment today!', 'Visit us online at <URL>, a Bigos Management Property.', 'Contact us at', 'show contact info', '...This amazing home will not be on the market long!', 'Monday: 9AM - 6PM', 'Tuesday: 9AM - 6PM', 'Wednesday: 9AM - 6PM', 'Thursday: 9AM - 6PM', 'Friday: 9AM - 5PM', 'Saturday: 10AM - 5PM', 'Sunday: CLOSED', '** BRING IN A COPY OF THIS AD AND RECEIVE $150 OFF YOUR FIRST MONTH RENT **']
